headline.print_headline: PSV Clinch Europa League Place, Champions Ajax Held
headline.main: PSV Clinch Europa League Place, Champions Ajax Held

lead_paragraph: PSV Eindhoven made sure of European club competition next season with a 2-0 win over NAC Breda while Ajax Amsterdam closed their Dutch championship-winning season with a draw on Saturday.
